    },
    "Your meditation history, mood data, post-session reflections, program progress, offline content, and preferences are stored locally on your device using Apple's secure SwiftData storage. Downloaded offline packs are stored in the App's sandboxed storage on your device. iCloud-synced data is encrypted in transit and at rest by Apple. Health data is written to Apple Health and governed by Apple's privacy framework. We do not operate external servers that store your personal data." : {

